    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small two-headed axes used for cutting mortises; one end is chisel-shaped and the other is a triangular knife.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
